To use:

  gem install saucelabs-adapter --source gems.pivotallabs.com

  cd your_project

  script/generate saucelabs_adapter

  If you are not using JsUnit, you can delete the following:
    tests/jsunit/jsunit_test_example.rb
    lib/tasks/jsunit.rake
    jsunit stanzas from config/selenium.yml

Install the python script dependencies with:

  If you don't have Python easy_install installed, go get it:

  curl -O http://peak.telecommunity.com/dist/ez_setup.py
  sudo python ez_setup.py

  then...

  sudo easy_install httplib2 simplejson twisted pycrypto

How to run Selenium Test::Unit tests locally and at Saucelabs.com:

  rake selenium:local

  rake selenium:sauce

How to run JsUnit tests locally and at Saucelabs.com:

  rake jsunit:selenium_rc:local

  rake jsunit:selenium_rc:sauce
